data.description: Back on the Market...NO FAULT of seller.  What a sweet place to call home.  This wonderful corner lot boasts awesome trees for shade.  The paved driveway is an added bonus.  Detached garage has a concrete floor, 2 bays for vehicles and one for lawnmowers, and storage area.  The deck is large and inviting and a great place to entertain your kids or your friends.  Added utility shed makes a great storage area, too.  This adorable home has custom cabinets, some laminate floors, and ceramic tiles in bathroom.  Large master with carpeting. Meticulously kept home.  Stove, refrigerator, dishwasher, microwave, washer and dryer all stay. Don't miss out on this great home.  See today!
